## üß© **Project Setup**

| Command                            | Description                                                       |
| ---------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `git init`                         | Initialize a new Git repository in your project folder.           |
| `git clone <repo-url>`             | Copy (clone) an existing remote repository to your local machine. |
| `git remote add origin <repo-url>` | Connect your local repo to a remote one (e.g., GitHub, GitLab).   |
| `git remote -v`                    | Show remote repository URLs.                                      |

