## üîÑ **Syncing & Updating**

| Command                    | Description                                          |
| -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| `git fetch`                | Download latest changes from remote without merging. |
| `git pull`                 | Fetch and merge latest changes into current branch.  |
| `git push`                 | Push your commits to remote repository.              |
| `git push origin <branch>` | Push a specific branch.                              |

