## üßπ **Undo & Fix Mistakes**

| Command                       | Description                                           |
| ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| `git restore <file>`          | Undo changes in a file (revert to last commit).       |
| `git restore --staged <file>` | Unstage a file before committing.                     |
| `git reset --hard HEAD`       | Reset everything to the last commit (‚ö† irreversible). |
| `git revert <commit-id>`      | Create a new commit that undoes a specific commit.    |
| `git log`                     | View commit history.                                  |
| `git diff`                    | Show changes not yet staged.                          |

