## üë• **Collaboration**

| Command                         | Description                                                |
| ------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| `git pull origin main`          | Update local main with latest changes from team.           |
| `git push origin feature/login` | Push your feature branch for review.                       |
| `git merge main`                | Merge main into your feature branch (before pull request). |
| `git stash`                     | Temporarily save unfinished work.                          |
| `git stash pop`                 | Restore stashed work.                                      |

