## üí° Pro Tips

* Always **pull before pushing** to avoid merge conflicts.
* Use **meaningful commit messages** (e.g., `"Fix login bug in AuthController"`).
* Create **feature branches** (`feature/new-ui`) instead of committing directly to `main`.
* Regularly **push your work** to remote ‚Äî don‚Äôt rely only on local commits.

